snippet: Gatlin won the 100 meters at the Diamond League opener in Doha, Qatar, in 9.74 seconds, a new meet record.
abstract: Justin Gatlin wins 100 meters at Diamond League opener in Doha, Qatar; looks forward to racing Usain Bolt at world championships in Beijing.
lead_paragraph: Gatlin won the 100 meters at the Diamond League opener in Doha, Qatar, in 9.74 seconds, a new meet record.
